lead_paragraph: Australia captured Pakistan's last two wickets to win the first day-night test in Brisbane by 39 runs before tea on day five on Monday but the touring side won huge admiration for their dogged fourth innings chase.

headline.print_headline: Australia Win First Test by 39 Runs
